{"slideshow_credits": null, "snippet": "Mandate employment checks, joined with a path to legalization.", "abstract": "Op-Ed article by former Sen Alan K Simpson and former Rep Bruce A Morrison suggests that way out of immigration impasse begins with mandating E-Verify employment eligibility check system for all employers; maintains that by pairing this mandate with process for legalizing immigrants on case-by-case basis, both Republican and Democratic politicians will be less hesitant to compromise in order to take action.", "section_name": "Opinion", "print_page": "25", "document_type": "article", "byline": {"person": [{"lastname": "SIMPSON", "rank": 1, "firstname": "Alan", "role": "reported", "organization": "", "middlename": "K."}, {"lastname": "MORRISON", "rank": 2, "firstname": "Bruce", "role": "reported", "organization": "", "middlename": "A."}], "original": "By ALAN K. SIMPSON and BRUCE A. MORRISON", "contributor": ""}, "web_url": "http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/18/opinion/a-way-out-on-immigration-reform.html", "lead_paragraph": "Mandate employment checks, joined with a path to legalization.", "headline": {"print_headline": "A Way Out on Immigration Reform", "main": "A Way Out on Immigration Reform", "content_kicker": "Op-Ed Contributors", "kicker": "Op-Ed Contributors"}, "_id": "5509277238f0d819240d12f6", "word_count": "846", "multimedia": [{"height": 126, "url": "images/2015/03/18/opinion/18Simpson/18Simpson-thumbWide.jpg", "legacy": {"wideheight": "126", "wide": "images/2015/03/18/opinion/18Simpson/18Simpson-thumbWide.jpg", "widewidth": "190"}, "subtype": "wide", "width": 190, "type": "image"}, {"height": 900, "url": "images/2015/03/18/opinion/18Simpson/18Simpson-articleLarge.jpg", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/03/18/opinion/18Simpson/18Simpson-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": "600", "xlargeheight": "900"}, "subtype": "xlarge", "width": 600, "type": "image"}, {"height": 75, "url": "images/2015/03/18/opinion/18Simpson/18Simpson-thumbStandard.jpg", "leg